com.sri.ai.grinder.theory.differencearithmetic

Interface RangeAndExceptionsSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>, Expression, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    RangeAndExceptionsSet.DefaultRangeAndExceptionsSet, RangeAndExceptionsSet.Empty, RangeAndExceptionsSet.Singleton

    @Beta
public interface RangeAndExceptionsSet
extends Expression
    An interface representing a set of integers by keeping the symbolic extremes of an aboveAndUpTo and a set of expressions in the aboveAndUpTo but not in the denoted set.
    Author:
    braz
